name: One Last Round (Brie Y. R., ssssybil, HA7Oes)
name_original: One Last Round (Brie Y. R., ssssybil, HA7Oes)
description:
This game is made in 3 weeks for Ludum Dare 50 Game Jam Extra. The theme is "Delay the Inevitable".

- How to Play -   

Left-Click to Choose   

Right-Click to Cancel     

Click "Play" at top-right corner to proceed and see whether you've delayed the inevitable!     

- Credits -     

BrieYR : Programming, Technical Art, Level Design, Narrative Design     

HA7Oes : Concept Art, Level Art, UI Art, Animation, Narrative Design     

Sybil : Music Composing, Sound Design, Voiceover Art, Narrative Design
